    <item>
      <title>美国官员就中国芯片限制向荷兰政府施压</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/us-officials-to-pressure-dutch-government-on-china-chip-curbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着拜登政府加大力度挫败北京的科技野心，美国高级官员计划下周访问荷兰，向荷兰政府施压，要求其加强对中国芯片设备的限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/us-officials-to-pressure-dutch-government-on-china-chip-curbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 14:15:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国极右翼议员否认从亲俄媒体处收受现金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/german-far-right-mp-denies-taking-cash-from-pro-russian-media</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国极右翼政党选择党的一名议员否认从一家捷克亲俄媒体那里收受资金，并指责布拉格政府开展诽谤活动，旨在影响六月欧洲议会选举的结果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/german-far-right-mp-denies-taking-cash-from-pro-russian-media</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 13:50:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于担心国家救援，泰晤士水务公司的更安全债券开始下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/thames-water-s-safer-bonds-start-to-drop-on-state-rescue-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰晤士水务公司接受国家救助的可能性越来越大，这给此前被认为不会受到该公用事业公司困境影响的债务带来压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/thames-water-s-safer-bonds-start-to-drop-on-state-rescue-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 13:43:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>安哥拉法院推翻多斯桑托斯儿子的贪污罪判决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/angola-court-overturns-dos-santos-son-s-graft-conviction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[安哥拉宪法法院推翻了前总统之子何塞·菲洛梅诺·多斯桑托斯在价值 5 亿美元的贪污案中的定罪，理由是侵犯了他获得公平审判的权利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/angola-court-overturns-dos-santos-son-s-graft-conviction</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 13:37:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北约盟国敦促谨慎对待基辅1000亿美元援助计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/nato-allies-urge-caution-over-100-billion-aid-plan-for-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北约盟国正在控制对拟议的 1000 亿美元资金支持乌克兰的可行性的预期，因为北约正在努力解决如何向基辅提供足够援助的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/nato-allies-urge-caution-over-100-billion-aid-plan-for-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 12:18:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
