      <title>南非前议长因贪污案获准保释</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/south-africa-s-former-speaker-hands-herself-over-to-authorities</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前议长诺西维韦·马皮萨-恩卡库拉因贪污指控出庭后，南非一家法院批准她保释。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/south-africa-s-former-speaker-hands-herself-over-to-authorities</guid>
